      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained with no expense spared. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster without a single blemish, and the interior is spotless, smelling and looking brand new. Mechanically, it performs flawlessly, offering a driving experience identical to the day it left the lot. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle in perfect condition.",
