    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic fixer-upper with potential? This car is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little TLC! While it shows significant wear and will need both mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic, low-cost entry point for a handy buyer. Grab this bargain today and turn it into your own custom creation!",
