    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, budget-friendly option for a buyer who doesn't mind some visible wear. While the engine starts reliably and the car is fully drivable, there are noticeable cosmetic imperfections, including minor body scuffs and some interior upholstery wear. It has been a steady performer, though the next owner should expect to perform some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it running smoothly. It\u2019s a practical choice for someone prioritizing utility over a showroom finish.",
      "price": 19500.0,
